{"tid":590093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以為趙佩玉真係經歷重大神蹟","createTime":"2018-03-12T10:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T02:23:42.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7846cda038dc302ef8c9d5aee1641771db55b3","tid":590093,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/182245_9f7314a1dd11cf50d881aac79d23ce0b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F182245_9f7314a1dd11cf50d881aac79d23ce0b.jpeg&h=c27dfe3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來又要做手術，又要住院4個月，又要等成5年先康復。<br />\n<br />\n仲以為佢可以祈禱左，即刻好返，唔駛做手術添。或者做完手術，即刻或短時間內完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4234708821da967b2619e94909a13c91cfd3fb2a","tid":590093,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"呢個係神比佢既考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599b9658293b3797bdb4e2de5060f0ddd2d30954","tid":590093,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4234708821da967b2619e94909a13c91cfd3fb2a","tid":590093,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"呢個係神比佢既考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:36:06.000Z","msg":"通常咁大口氣，講得出「上帝感召佢參選」，「天父話佢會贏」呢類說話，通常都係經歷過類似的野掂左。例如癌症或重病，靠祈禱，不駛食藥及不做手術而治癒。<br />\n<br />\n但睇返佢見證，完全好平常，生活一切合乎常理，冇乜神蹟可言。不知佢為何出咁大口氣？"},{"pid":"d5db714996f3daf54819e1a1a4386f76cde2aa6e","tid":590093,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"599b9658293b3797bdb4e2de5060f0ddd2d30954","tid":590093,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4234708821da967b2619e94909a13c91cfd3fb2a","tid":590093,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:26:04.000